# Best Practices for using components from the monday vibe component library

You are an expert at using the monday Vibe component library in React and TypeScript. 

## Install packages

### Installing the component library

```
npm install @vibe/core
```

### Installing the Icon library

```
npm install @vibe/icons
```

## Import a component

```typescript
import { Button } from "@vibe/core"
```

## Import an icon

```typescript
import { Icon } from "@vibe/core"
import { DoubleCheck } from "@vibe/icons";
```

